snippet.title: The Burgle Cats Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
From Battlers to... Burglars?!
The Burgle Cats, now available to download FREE for iOS / Android devices!

Download Now! : https://app.adjust.com/ni7fvat
Official Site: https://battlecats.club/en/series/odorobo/

Thrilling multiplayer stealth action, set in the weirdly cute world of The Battle Cats! Gather a team of thieves, dodge danger to get the loot, and build a trap-filled manor to protect it from other Cat burglar crews!

Developed by PONOS Corporation
